            </div>
            <div class="asg-fig">
                <div class="n">3</div>
                <div class="l">brenda u portfelju</div>
                <div class="d">STO &middot; XYPEX &middot; CORTEC</div>
            </div>
            <div class="asg-fig">
                <div class="n">100%</div>
                <div class="l">tehnička podrška</div>
                <div class="d">Inženjer prati svaki projekat</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ====================================================
     05 PROJECTS
     ==================================================== -->
<section class="asg-section">
    <div class="asg-wrap">
        <div class="asg-shead">
            <div class="asg-num">05 — Projekti</div>
            <div>
                <h2 class="asg-h2">Realizovani projekti, ne render slike.</h2>
                <p class="asg-lede">Selekcija nedavnih radova — od stambenih kompleksa do hidroelektrana.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="asg-proj-grid">
            <article class="asg-proj">
                <div class="asg-ph" style="height:340px">[ stambeni / mostar, bih ]</div>
                <div class="meta"><span>Stambeni</span><span>2024</span></div>
                <h3>Stambeno-poslovni kompleks — Mostar</h3>
                <div class="s">STO ETICS &middot; MW 16cm &middot; 4.200 m² &middot; Mostar, BiH</div>
            </article>
            <article class="asg-proj">
                <div class="asg-ph" style="height:340px">[ industrijski / jablanica, bih ]</div>
                <div class="meta"><span>Industrijski</span><span>2024</span></div>
                <h3>Hidroelektrana — sanacija temelja</h3>
                <div class="s">XYPEX Concentrate + Patch &middot; 1.800 m² &middot; Jablanica, BiH</div>
            </article>
            <article class="asg-proj">
                <div class="asg-ph" style="height:340px">[ javni / tomislavgrad, bih ]</div>
                <div class="meta"><span>Javni</span><span>2023</span></div>
                <h3>Osnovna škola — energetska obnova</h3>
                <div class="s">STO ETICS &middot; EPS 15cm &middot; 2.600 m² &middot; Tomislavgrad, BiH</div>
            </article>
            <article class="asg-proj">
                <div class="asg-ph" style="height:340px">[ industrijski / livno, bih ]</div>
                <div class="meta"><span>Industrijski</span><span>2023</span></div>
