                <div class="s">XYPEX Admix + Megamix &middot; 800 m³ &middot; Livno, BiH</div>
            </article>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top:48px; text-align:center;">
            <a href="/projects" class="asg-btn asg-btn-sec">
                Svi projekti
                <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7" />
                </svg>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ====================================================
     06 TESTIMONIALS
     ==================================================== -->
<section class="asg-section asg-soft">
    <div class="asg-wrap">
        <div class="asg-shead">
            <div class="asg-num">06 — Reference</div>
            <div>
                <h2 class="asg-h2">Šta kažu ljudi koji su radili sa nama.</h2>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="asg-test-grid">
            <article class="asg-test">
                <div class="quote">ASGifiks tim nam je obezbijedio kompletnu tehničku dokumentaciju i podršku tokom ugradnje. Projekat smo završili u roku, bez improvizacije.</div>
                <div class="author">
                    <div>
                        <div class="n">Ivan Marković</div>
                        <div class="r">Inženjer gradnje</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="c">GP Hercegovina d.o.o.</div>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="asg-test">
                <div class="quote">XYPEX je riješio problem prokišnjavanja garaže koji nismo uspjeli sanirati klasičnim hidroizolacijama. Dvije godine bez kapi vode.</div>
                <div class="author">
                    <div>
                        <div class="n">Anela Dautović</div>
                        <div class="r">Upravnik objekta</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="c">Stambena zajednica BB</div>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="asg-test">
                <div class="quote">Pouzdana isporuka, korektne cijene, i — što je najvažnije — ljudi koji znaju o čemu pričaju. Drugi distributeri nude proizvod, ASGifiks nudi rješenje.</div>
                <div class="author">
                    <div>
                        <div class="n">Marin Galić</div>
                        <div class="r">Direktor</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="c">Galić Gradnja d.o.o.</div>
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ====================================================
     07 CERTIFICATIONS
     ==================================================== -->
<section class="asg-section asg-tight">
    <div class="asg-wrap">
        <div style="margin-bottom:32px; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:baseline; gap:24px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <div class="asg-eyebrow"><span class="dot"></span>Certifikati i standardi</div>
            <div style="font-size:14px; color:var(--asg-muted); max-width:42ch;">
                Svi materijali u našem portfelju imaju neophodne EU sertifikate i deklaracije za primjenu na bh. tržištu.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="asg-cert-grid">
            <div class="asg-cert"><div class="n">ISO 9001</div><div class="d">Sistem upravljanja kvalitetom</div></div>
            <div class="asg-cert"><div class="n">CE oznaka</div><div class="d">EU usklađenost materijala</div></div>
            <div class="asg-cert"><div class="n">NSF/ANSI 61</div><div class="d">XYPEX — pitka voda</div></div>
            <div class="asg-cert"><div class="n">EPD</div><div class="d">Environmental Product Declaration</div></div>
            <div class="asg-cert"><div class="n">STO Partner</div><div class="d">Ovlašteni distributer</div></div>
            <div class="asg-cert"><div class="n">XYPEX Auth.</div><div class="d">Sertificirani distributer</div></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ====================================================
     08 FAQ
     ==================================================== -->
<section class="asg-section">
    <div class="asg-wrap">
        <div class="asg-faq-grid">
            <div>
                <div class="asg-num" style="display:inline-block; margin-bottom:16px;">09 — Pitanja</div>
                <h2 class="asg-h2">Često postavljana.</h2>
                <p class="asg-lede" style="margin-top:16px;">
                    Ne nalazite odgovor? Pišite nam na info@asgifiks.ba ili pozovite.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="asg-faq-list">
                @foreach (var (faq, i) in _faqs.Select((f, i) => (f, i)))
                {
                    <div class="asg-faq-item">
                        <div class="asg-faq-q @(_openFaq == i ? "open" : "")" @onclick="() => ToggleFaq(i)">
                            <span>@faq.Q</span>
                            <span class="ic">
                                @if (_openFaq == i)
                                {
                                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round">
                                        <path d="M5 12h14" />
                                    </svg>
                                }
                                else
                                {
                                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round">
                                        <path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14" />
                                    </svg>
                                }
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        @if (_openFaq == i)
                        {
                            <div class="asg-faq-a">@faq.A</div>
                        }
                    </div>
                }
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ====================================================
     10 CTA (dark)
     ==================================================== -->
<section class="asg-section asg-dark asg-tight">
    <div class="asg-wrap">
        <div class="asg-cta-grid">
            <div>
                <h2 style="font-size:clamp(36px,4.5vw,64px); line-height:1; letter-spacing:-.025em; font-weight:700; margin:0; color:var(--asg-paper);">
                    Spreman si <em style="font-style:normal; color:var(--asg-slate);">specificirati</em> sistem?
                </h2>
                <p style="color:rgba(244,241,234,.7); font-size:17px; margin:16px 0 0; max-width:48ch;">
